{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"61e70fd8-ec6c-424e-9db0-1c4faddc6086","content":"No files found in the working directory. I'll provide you with the solution directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?>\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Slider Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"48\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** the `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` attribute tells the XAML compiler to resolve all `{Binding …}` paths against that type at compile time.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Treat invalid bindings as build errors instead of warnings -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nWith compiled bindings + strict compilation enabled:\n\n- A typo like `{Binding Themee}` becomes a **compiler error** (e.g., `XC0045: Property 'Themee' not found on 'SettingsViewModel'`).\n- Type mismatches (binding an `int` property to a `string`-only control) are also flagged.\n\n**Tips:**\n- You can scope `x:DataType` to any element (e.g., a `DataTemplate`) — it doesn't have to be on the root.\n- Use `x:DataType=\"x:Null\"` on a subtree to opt out where dynamic bindings are needed.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"fe432c14-c980-47e0-ba4f-234a8a512c48","outputTokens":555,"requestId":"5038:1E6E:181F8B6:1ADDC39:69FA8FB0"},"id":"faa2c725-1670-47ad-bbeb-803974a38e6f","timestamp":"2026-05-06T00:47:55.367Z","parentId":"24fe3f31-a5f7-4c6b-9b0a-a0a07b4607a1"}
